description:
This is a 13 minute workout called 'Awesome Kids and Beginners Cycling Workout...  Rollers, Static Trainer or Even Stabilisers!' from the channel Ruby Isaac.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Hi all you awesome kids.... here is my first cycling exercise video...

Here is Stage 1 of Tour De Kids....

You can do it on rollers... a turbo trainer..... or even just put shoes under your stabilisers....

If you like it please let me know on Instagram at @rubywisaac and I will do another one...

Oh and mind out for those ducks!!!!!

Stay awesome!!!!


Ruby X...
